message:
My call history is full to bursting.
<?>
All the calls are from Koujaku.

name: 紅雀
message: "You didn't pick up! I was going crazy here!"

name: 蒼葉
message: "I just got a little tied up... I'm heading back now. I'll explain when I see you."

name: 紅雀
message: "Got it. I'm at Hum-Drum Junk right now, so I'll meet you there."
The sound of Koujaku's voice has brought me back to reality.
Dry Juice, Granny... my kidnapping and near-rape...
It felt like a nightmare. But no, it was all real.
I down some pills, pick up my bag, and leave the room.
